<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“二十三，二十四，”阿拉丁数着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又走了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“二十五。”楼梯很黑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定要很小心。”他轻轻地对自己说，“三十。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快阿拉丁在黑暗中看到了一些东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“光。”他慢慢向下走的时候说，“四十二。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>光变得越来越亮了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“四十八，四十九。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上就要到了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“五十！”阿拉丁走进了一个很小的门，他看了看周围。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那个黄金房间！”他大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里有四个黄金罐子，就像马格里布说的那样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要碰任何东西。”阿拉丁提醒自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那个时候，风吹过了他的脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么？”他很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵强风把他的腰带吹到了一个黄金罐子那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！”阿拉丁说，他把他的腰带拉了回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道这里是不是有精灵。”他小声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的帽子被吹走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“停住！”他跳起来抓帽子的时候对着空气说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跨过了那扇门，差一点碰到了一个黄金罐子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁吸了一口气。“真是太险了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁拿着他的帽子，跑向了在他面前的一扇大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的名字是阿拉丁！”他大声说，“我命令你开门！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那扇门突然开了，阿拉丁走进了一个美丽的花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>空气中有花香和果实的味道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向上看。“橘子！”他说，“柠檬和橙子！梨子和梅子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁饿了。他希望他可以吃一个梅子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的表情突然变得开心起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父说拿到了灯，把所有的水果都摘了也可以！”他心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>花园的路就在他的脚下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一，二，三。”他一边在树间走着一边数着自己的步子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在一百步之后，阿拉丁到了有梯子的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向上看了看。梯子的顶端被藏在树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁慢慢地往上爬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他到了最上面的时候，他看到墙上的洞在阴影里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是可以看到洞里挂在链子上的灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出手拿走了灯，然后把灯拿在手里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这只是一个又脏又旧的铜灯，”他摇摇头说，“我不想要弄脏我的外套。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁用腰带把灯包了起来，然后把它卷起来放在了后面的口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他从梯子上爬了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了。”他说，“我要找一些东西吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是当阿拉丁回到地面的时候，他无法相信他看到的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些橘子、柠檬和橙子都不见了。梨子和梅子也都不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而，果树上面都挂满了亮晶晶的珠宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“水果都变成玻璃了！”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摘了一颗亮红色的珠宝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能吃这个东西。”他耸了耸肩说，“但是它好漂亮。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要摘一些玻璃水果带回家给妈妈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁年纪很小，他一直都很穷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不知道这些东西是珍贵的宝石——翡翠、钻石和红宝石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们根本不是玻璃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他开始把珠宝装进衣服和裤子的口袋里，直到珠宝把口袋都装满了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，我必须回去找伯父了。”他对自己说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他急忙地穿过了黄金房间，然后开始向马格里布走回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁装了太重的东西，他几乎不能爬上石阶了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他快要到顶端的时候，他爬不上最后那个最高的台阶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父。”他喊道，“我回来了，快帮帮我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>